text: The 2016 WDF Europe Cup was the 20th edition of the WDF Europe Cup darts tournament, organised by the World Darts Federation. It was held in Egmond aan Zee, Netherlands from September 20 to 24. __TOC__ ==Entered Teams== 32 countries/associations entered a men's selection in the event. 26 countries/associations entered a womans's selection in the event. | style="width: 50%;text-align: left; vertical-align: top; " | {| class="wikitable" |- !
